title: DDFP 287: Week 1 picks

description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Elliot Harrison to rehash the Packers vs. Seahawks game and do their “Red Challenge Flag Picks” segment with a few of the opening weekend games as well as their picks for all of week 1.
